column1: patientlights 130627347588 "2015-10-06 17:42:58 GMT" http://patientlights.tumblr.com/post/130627347588/dear-taylor-swift-im-sorry-for-my-sexism "ameliastardust:Hey guys
column2: so my rad friend Randy just wrote a sort of “open letter” to @taylorswift about her music; it focuses specifically on what it’s like to listen to a female pop star as a heterosexual male and how as we grow older
column3: we realize just how much the casual misogyny ingrained in popular culture affects our views and opinions. As Taylor Swift herself put it: “a man writing about his feelings from a vulnerable place is brave; a woman writing about her feelings from a vulnerable place is oversharing or whining”. Randy’s article illustrates this point perfectly
column4: and is a brutally honest telling of what it took for him to fully understand this. Please give it a read and let him know what you think!" False link
